OL,3,CMan remanded in custody over 'sweets
OL,4,Callegedly laced with sedatives'
OL,6,FThe court was told the charges relate
OL,7,Fto sweets which were allegedly laced
OL,8,Fwith sedatives.
OL,10,FLeicestershire Police received a
OL,11,Freport on Sunday that children at
OL,12,FStathern Lodge in Canal Lane,
OL,13,FStathern, had become ill.
OL,15,FEight children, all boys aged between
OL,16,Feight and 11, and one adult were taken
OL,17,Fto hospital as a precaution, but were
OL,18,Fdischarged, police said.
