OL,3,CMan remanded in custody over 'sweets
OL,4,Callegedly laced with sedatives'
OL,6,FThe defendant, who stood in the dock
OL,7,Fwearing a grey sweatshirt, spoke only
OL,8,Fto confirm his name, date of birth and
OL,9,Faddress during the four-minute hearing.
OL,11,FRuben was told by chair of the
OL,12,Fmagistrates Elizabeth Needham that he
OL,13,Fwill appear at Leicester Crown Court
OL,14,Fon August 29.
OL,16,FHe gave no indication of his pleas
OL,17,Fduring the hearing on Saturday.
