OL,3,CMan remanded in custody over 'sweets
OL,4,Callegedly laced with sedatives'
OL,6,FRuben was arrested on Monday evening
OL,7,Fat a nearby pub on suspicion of
OL,8,Fadministering poison or a noxious
OL,9,Fthing with intent to injure, aggrieve
OL,10,For annoy.
OL,12,FPolice said the "owners and operators
OL,13,Fof Stathern Lodge are independent from
OL,14,Fthose people who use or hire the lodge
OL,15,Fand are not connected to the incident".
OL,17,FThe lodge is a converted farmhouse
OL,18,Fwith a sports hall and catering
OL,19,Ffacilities. The investigation is being
OL,20,Fled by the East Midlands special
OL,21,Foperations unit's major incident team.
