OL,6,FLeicestershire Police has referred
OL,7,Fitself to the Independent Office for
OL,8,FPolice Conduct after officers said the
OL,9,Fincident happened on Monday, before
OL,10,Famending the date to Sunday.
OL,12,FIt is still unclear when officers
OL,13,Fresponded and whether that is why the
OL,14,Fwatchdog referral has been made.
OL,16,FNeighbours described seeing distressed
OL,17,Fparents outside the village hall in
OL,18,Fnearby Plungar, which was used as a
OL,19,Ftriage centre for the children on
OL,20,FMonday.
